haw.livingplace.scriptSimulator.script

Interface Scriptable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Scriptable>, java.lang.Runnable, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BedEntry, DoorBellEntry, DoorEntry, OnOffEntry, PeriodicEntry, Script, ScriptEntry, SensorEntry, SingleEntry, TemperaturSensorEntry, UbisenseEntry, UbisenseMockupEntry, UbisenseToolsEntry, WindowEntry

    public interface Scriptable
extends java.lang.Runnable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Scriptable>
    The Scriptable interface extends the Runnable interface and defines methods which have to be implemented by an entry for the Script class.
    Author:
    Andreas Basener
